      "id": "txt34",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 690,
      "y": 308,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 140,
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "make_core_step_table(data)\n1  raw.rename(legacy->native)      [legacy_to_native_raw]\n2  pl.from_pandas -> native polars raw\n3  engine: summarizers.make_step_table (+ C-rate expr)\n4  to_pandas + rename(native->legacy) [native_to_legacy_step]\n5  reorder to legacy column order (byte-for-byte oracle)\n6  legacy sort + 'index' column; map spec 'info' in pandas\n->  data.steps  (legacy pandas)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "rect33",
      "originalText": "make_core_step_table(data)\n1  raw.rename(legacy->native)      [legacy_to_native_raw]\n2  pl.from_pandas -> native polars raw\n3  engine: summarizers.make_step_table (+ C-rate expr)\n4  to_pandas + rename(native->legacy) [native_to_legacy_step]\n5  reorder to legacy column order (byte-for-byte oracle)\n6  legacy sort + 'index' column; map spec 'info' in pandas\n->  data.steps  (legacy pandas)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 136,
      "index": "aX",
      "autoResize": true
