      "type": "text",
      "x": 690,
      "y": 548,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 158,
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "make_core_summary(data)\n1  raw AND steps rename(legacy->native)\n2  polars: make_summary + ir_to_summary + c_rates_to_summary\n    (IR / C-rate native names == legacy names: survive rename)\n3  to_pandas + rename(native->legacy) [native_to_legacy_summary]\n4  merge date_time back from legacy raw (native: epoch only)\n5  _add_legacy_summary_cruft: cumulated CE, shifted caps, RIC\n6  reorder to legacy summary column order\n->  data.summary  (legacy pandas)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "rect35",
      "originalText": "make_core_summary(data)\n1  raw AND steps rename(legacy->native)\n2  polars: make_summary + ir_to_summary + c_rates_to_summary\n    (IR / C-rate native names == legacy names: survive rename)\n3  to_pandas + rename(native->legacy) [native_to_legacy_summary]\n4  merge date_time back from legacy raw (native: epoch only)\n5  _add_legacy_summary_cruft: cumulated CE, shifted caps, RIC\n6  reorder to legacy summary column order\n->  data.summary  (legacy pandas)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 154,
