      "text": "add_scaled_summary_columns(data)\n1  summary.rename(legacy->native)\n2  polars: equivalent_cycles + generate_specific_summary_columns\n3  rename extended per mode:  '{col}_{mode}' -> '{legacy_col}_{mode}'\n    (gravimetric / areal / absolute)\n->  data.summary  (legacy pandas)",
