      "text": "polars engines (summarizers.py)\nmake_step_table -> per-step statistics\n    <signal>_<stat>  (mean, std, min, max, first, last, delta)\nmake_summary -> per-cycle CycleCols subset\nir_to_summary,  c_rates_to_summary,\nequivalent_cycles_to_summary,\ngenerate_specific_summary_columns",
