      "id": "txt59",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1470,
      "y": 1198,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 146,
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "Guarantees (tests/test_header_mapping.py)\n- STAT_SUFFIXES + pair lists bijective\n- round-trip identity:\n    legacy -> native -> legacy == id\n- totality: every column is mapped OR in\n  a NATIVE_ONLY_* / LEGACY_ONLY_* set\n  (new columns fail the test until categorised)\n- bridge parity: the bridge's rename dicts\n  are exactly the mapping-derived dicts",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "rect58",
      "originalText": "Guarantees (tests/test_header_mapping.py)\n- STAT_SUFFIXES + pair lists bijective\n- round-trip identity:\n    legacy -> native -> legacy == id\n- totality: every column is mapped OR in\n  a NATIVE_ONLY_* / LEGACY_ONLY_* set\n  (new columns fail the test until categorised)\n- bridge parity: the bridge's rename dicts\n  are exactly the mapping-derived dicts",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 142,
      "index": "aw",
      "autoResize": true
    },
